'''五氟化氯'''（Chlorine pentafluoride）化學式为ClF<sub>5</sub>，是[[氟|氟]]和[[氯|氯]]的化合物，也是一种[[互卤化物|互卤化物]]，首次合成於1963年。<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Smith D. F.
| title = Chlorine Pentafluoride
| journal = [[Science_(journal)|Science]]
| year = 1963
| volume = 141
| issue = 3585
| pages = 1039–1040
| doi = 10.1126/science.141.3585.1039
| pmid = 17739492}}</ref> 这种无色气体是一种强[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]，曾经是火箭的候选氧化剂。

它具有C<sub>4v</sub>对称性的[[四方锥|四方锥]]结构<ref>{{Greenwood&Earnshaw2nd|page=833}}</ref>已经被高清晰度的<sup>19</sup>F[[核磁共振|核磁共振]]所证实。<ref name=Pilipovich>{{cite journal
|author1=Pilipovich, D. |author2=Maya, W. |author3=Lawton, E.A. |author4=Bauer, H.F. |author5=Sheehan, D. F. |author6=Ogimachi, N. N. |author7=Wilson, R. D. |author8=Gunderloy, F. C. |author9=Bedwell, V. E. | title = Chlorine pentafluoride. Preparation and Properties
| journal = [[Inorganic_Chemistry_(journal)|Inorganic Chemistry]]
| year = 1967
| volume = 6
| issue = 10
| pages = 1918
| doi = 10.1021/ic50056a036}}</ref>

== 制备 ==

五氟化氯的一些早期合成得到了分类。 <ref name=Clark>{{Cite book
| title = Ignition! An Informal History of Liquid Rocket Propellants
| url = http://www.sciencemadness.org/library/books/ignition.pdf
| last = Clark
| first = John D.
| authorlink = John Drury Clark
| publisher = Rutgers University Press
| year = 1972
| pages = 87–88
| isbn = 0-8135-0725-1
| access-date = 2020-10-20
| archive-date = 2020-05-15
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200515200547/http://www.sciencemadness.org/library/books/ignition.pdf
| dead-url = no
}}</ref><ref name=Smith>{{cite journal
|author = Smith D. F.
| title = Chlorine Pentafluoride
| journal = [[Science_(journal)|Science]]
| year = 1963
| volume = 141
| issue = 3585
| pages = 1039–1040
| doi = 10.1126/science.141.3585.1039
| pmid = 17739492}}</ref>最初，一种常用于合成五氟化氯的方法是[[三氟化氯|ClF<sub>3</sub>]]与[[氟|F<sub>2</sub>]]在高温高压下反应。<ref name=Clark /> 
:ClF<sub>3</sub>  +  F<sub>2</sub>   →   ClF<sub>5</sub>
:ClF  +  2F<sub>2</sub>   →   ClF<sub>5</sub>
:Cl<sub>2</sub>  +  5F<sub>2</sub>   →   2ClF<sub>5</sub>
:CsClF<sub>4</sub>  +  F<sub>2</sub>   →   CsF  +  ClF<sub>5</sub>

此外，金属氟化物即MClF<sub>4</sub>(例如KClF<sub>4</sub>, RbClF<sub>4</sub>, CsClF<sub>4</sub>)与F<sub>2</sub>的反应产生ClF<sub>5</sub>和相应的金属[[氟化物|氟化物]]MF。{{ref_label|Pilipovich|1|}} <ref name=Smith /> 1981年, 研究人员发现[[氟化镍|NiF<sub>2</sub>]]是一个很好的制备ClF<sub>5</sub>的[[催化剂|催化剂]]。<ref>{{cite journal
