| year = 1981
| volume = 17
| pages = 381–383
| doi = 10.1016/S0022-1139(00)81783-2}}</ref>

== 反應 ==

五氟化氯与[[水|水]]剧烈反應产生[[高氯酸氟|FClO<sub>4</sub>]]和[[氟化氢|HF]]<ref name="patnaik2007">{{cite book
| title = A comprehensive guide to the hazardous properties of chemical substances
| url = https://archive.org/details/comprehensivegui00prad_607
| author = Pradyot Patnaik
| edition = 3rd
| publisher = Wiley-Interscience
| year = 2007
| isbn = 0471714585
| pages = [https://archive.org/details/comprehensivegui00prad_607/page/n502 478]–479
}}</ref> 或是[[氯酰氟|氯酰氟]]和[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]：<ref>{{Greenwood&Earnshaw2nd|page=834}}</ref>
:{{chem|ClF|5}} + 2 {{chem|H|2|O}} → {{chem|ClO|2|F}} + 4 {{chem|HF}}

另外，它也是一個強大的[[氟化劑|氟化劑]]。它在室温下就能很容易地与所有元素（包括一些“惰性”的元素，如 [[铂|铂]]和[[金|金]]）反应，除了所有[[惰性气体|惰性气体]]、 [[氮|氮]]、 [[氧|氧]]和[[氟|氟]]。<ref name=Pilipovich />

